De_Operation_Alleyway_Mugging v1.0
-----------------------------------------------

This medium sized map is ideal for small servers and clan matches. 

The map welcomes smg's and shotguns into the playing field with its tight corners and enclosed areas, sniping also proves very dangerous as well. But watch out! There could be a mugger ready to knife you at any moment 
if your not cautious. 

The map has 40 spawn points and includes HDR.

Enjoy the map!
